ml.classification

Class LogisticRegressionByNonlinearConjugateGradient

  • java.lang.Object
    • ml.classification.Classifier
      • ml.classification.LogisticRegressionByNonlinearConjugateGradient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class LogisticRegressionByNonlinearConjugateGradient
extends Classifier
    Multi-class logistic regression by nonlinear conjugate gradient method.

    We aim to minimize the cross-entropy error function defined by

    E(W) = -ln{p(T|w1, w2,..., wK)} / N = -sum_n{sum_k{t_{nk}ln(v_nk)}} / N,

    where \nabla E(W) = X * (V - T) / N and v_nk = P(C_k|x_n).

    Version:
    1.0 Jan. 26th, 2014
    Author:
    Mingjie Qian
